Linux shell scripts collection
==============================


backup-home.sh
==============

Backup user's home folder to an external media, useful for weekly backups. EDIT BACKUP PATH VARIABLE BEFORE FIRST USE!


backup-root.sh
==============

Backup root folder to an external media, useful for weekly backups. EDIT BACKUP PATH VARIABLE BEFORE FIRST USE!


backup-www.sh
=============

Backup ~/www folder to an external media, useful for weekly backups. EDIT BACKUP PATH VARIABLE BEFORE FIRST USE!


cert-delete.sh
==============

Delete local CA certificate.


cert-import.sh
==============

Import remote CA certificate.


cert-list.sh
============

List local CA certificates.


detoxify.sh
===========

Remove special chars from filenames recursively and rename to lower filenames recursively.


fix-chrome-profile.sh
=====================

Fix current user's Chrome profile after Google Chrome crash.


delete-chrome-profile.sh
========================

Delete current user's Chrome profile after Google Chrome crash. ATTENTION - destructive operation!


pdf-check.sh
============

Check PDF files for validity recursively, rename invalid files.


restore-home.sh
===============

Restore user's home folder from an external media. ATTENTION - destructive operation!


restore-root.sh
===============

Restore root folder from an external media ATTENTION - destructive operation!


skype.sh
========

Run Skype with video support.


ssl-create.sh
=============

Create and setup self-signed SSL certificate for Apache2.


svn-create.sh
=============

Create subversion repository. EDIT SVN PATH VARIABLE BEFORE FIRST USE!


